{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0002", "text": "[Cybersecurity](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/veilig/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0002", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0003", "text": "As an entrepreneur you want to move forward. Serving new customers, streamlining your processes, strengthening your team. But in this digital age there is an invisible danger lurking: cyber attacks. They increasingly affect SMEs and can not only paralyze your systems, but also damage your reputation. Fortunately, there is now a way to better protect your company against these risks – with the help of the MCZ subsidy.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0003", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0004", "text": "Cybercrime is no longer something that only affects large companies. Small and medium-sized enterprises in particular are increasingly becoming targets. Why? Because they are often less secure, even though they manage valuable data and resources. A cyber attack can easily cause tens of thousands of euros in damage and often brings your business operations to a standstill.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0004", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0005", "text": "Investing in cybersecurity pays off. It not only prevents damage, but also gives your customers and employees confidence in the safety of your business environment.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0005", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0006", "text": "The government offers financial support with [the MCZ subsidy](https://www.rvo.nl/subsidies-financing/mcz). With this scheme you receive a 50% discount on cybersecurity investments, up to a maximum of €1,250. This allows you to take a maximum of €2,500 in security measures. An ideal step to strengthen your digital security.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0006", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0007", "text": "This subsidy is specifically intended for new investments, such as:", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0007", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0008", "text": "- securing your network and WiFi;\n- setting up two-factor authentication;\n- implementing backup systems;\n- offering cyber awareness training for your team.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0008", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0009", "text": "As a bank, we understand how important it is to make the right choices when it comes to cybersecurity. That is why we would like to think along with you. Our collaboration with recognized cybersecurity specialists, such as Threadstone, not only provides you with the right tools, but also the insights and guidance you need to keep your business secure.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0009", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0010", "text": "- an extensive risk inventory of your digital vulnerabilities;\n- training for your team to recognize and prevent cyber risks;\n- monitoring and detection to actively identify threats.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0010", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0011", "text": "This way you are not only prepared for the dangers of today, but also for the challenges of tomorrow.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0011", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0012", "text": "Your company must meet three conditions. Maximum 50 employees, less than € 10 million annual turnover and a Chamber of Commerce registration.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0012", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 12, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0013", "text": "The [CyberSafe Check](https://tools.digitaltrustcenter.nl/cyberveilig-check/) from the Digital Trust Center is mandatory. Complete this for the most relevant investments and download the advice as a PDF, without this document your application will be rejected.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0013", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 13, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0014", "text": "#### Step 3: Invest smartly in your digital security", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0014", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 14, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0015", "text": "Now you choose which measures you take. You do not have to immediately follow all the advice from the CyberSafe Check, but it is a good guideline. Our cybersecurity experts are happy to help you with this.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0015", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 15, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0016", "text": "Make sure your invoice contains all required information and preferably pay by bank for a direct bank statement.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0016", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 16, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0017", "text": "Registrations have been open since July 18, 2025. You can submit your application via RVO with your eHerkenning (minimum level 2+). The deadline is October 31, 2025.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0017", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 17, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0018", "text": "Curious how we can support you? View our cybersecurity solutions or contact our specialists. Together we make your company resilient to cyber threats.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0018", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 18, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0019", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0019", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 19, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0020", "text": "- Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs.\n- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks.\n- Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie__c4-paragraph__0020", "source_slug": "versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie", "source_title": "Strengthen your digital resilience with the MCZ subsidy", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/versterk-je-digitale-weerbaarheid-met-de-mcz-subsidie.html", "source_date": "2025-09-04", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 20, "n_chunks_total": 23, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
